l football team|Equatorial Guinea women's national team]].\n\n==Club career==\nPachu started with E. Waiso Ipola in the Equatoguinean women's football league. She moved to [[Vegetarianos FC|Leones Vegetarianos FC]] in 2018. She joined Spanish team El Ejido in the winter of 2019.\n\n==International career==\nPachu made her international debut for [[Equatorial Guinea women's national football team|Equatorial Guinea]] on 26 November 2017, coming on as a second-half [[Substitute (association football)|substitute]] in a 4\u20130 home friendly win against [[Comoros women's national football team|Comoros]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pachu}}\n[[Category:1986 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Equatoguinean women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Women's association football fullbacks]]\n[[Category:Equatorial Guinea women's international footballers]]\n[[Category:Equatoguinean expatriate women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Equatoguinean expatriate sportspeople in Spain]]\n[[Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Spain]]\n\n\n{{EquatorialGuinea-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|                name = Pachu\n|               image = \n|            fullname = Maricruz Mangue Oburu Nchama<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rfaf.es/pnfg/NPcd/NFG_VisEquipos?cod_primaria=1000119&Codigo_Equipo=13033013|accessdate=11 January 2019|publisher=RFAF|title=Visualizaci\u00f3n de Equipos}}</ref>\n|         birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1986|03|06}}<ref>[http://www.cafonline.com/en-us/competitions/11theditionwomenafcon-ghana2018.aspx/TeamDetails/playerdetails?CompetitionPlayerId=%2Bbg%2BE4hJSe1iRrEGaE9xRAooYDbcz%2BxnexRNEYu3i6BHo01%2BZBRH412W8elMsm8X Pachu] at the [[Confederation of African Football]] official website</ref>\n\n| birth_place = \n|              height = {{Height|m=1.51}}\n| position = [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|Left back]]\n|         currentclub = \n|          clubnumber = \n| years1 = 2012\u2